text.paragraph:
The mean bioavailability of gabapentin was reduced by about 20% with concomitant use of an antacid (Maalox
                              ®
                           ) containing magnesium and aluminum hydroxides.  It is recommended that gabapentin be taken at least 2 hours following Maalox administration [see Clinical Pharmacology (12.3)].
